</li><li><span id="22"></span>Hofbauer, R K; Rainville, P; Duncan, G H and Bushnell, M C (2001). Cortical representation of the sensory dimension of pain. <i>Journal of Neurophysiology</i> 86: 402-411.
</li><li><span id="8"></span>Inadomi, J M; Fennerty, M B and Bjorkman, D (2003). The economic impact of irritable bowel syndrome. <i>Alimentary Pharmacology &amp; Therapeutics</i> 18: 671-682.
</li><li><span id="11"></span>Kirwilliam, S S and Derbyshire, S W G (2008). Increased bias to report heat or pain following emotional priming of pain-related fear. <i>Pain</i> 137: 60-65.
