</li><li><span id="25"></span>Mannheim, K (1935). <i>Ideology and Utopia.</i> New York: Harcourt, Brace and Company.
</li><li><span id="10"></span>Macfarlane, G J; McBeth, J and Silman, A J (2001). Widespread body pain and mortality: prospective population based study. <i>British Medical Journal</i> 323: 1-4.
